{
  "texts": [
    "To confirm the effectiveness of the visual speech predictor, we have replaced the audio-based speech predictor with the visual speech predictor in our AVSR framework and evaluated its performance on a pre-trained model.",
    "The results, shown in Table 6, indicate that the visual speech rate predictor achieves a WER of 0.75%, which is nearly the same as the 0.72% obtained by the audio-based predictor.",
    "To evaluate the effectiveness of the proposed method on audio-unavailable scenarios, we have Method WER (%) w/ Speech rate predictor 0.72 w/ Visual speech rate predictor 0.75",
    "Table 6: Comparison between audio-based and visual speech rate predictors.",
    "conducted an additional experiment in which the proposed method was trained solely on the visual modality."
  ]
}